@VanLife.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7250

### Vans - get all (no filters)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans
Accept: application/json

### Vans - get all (category filter: Simple)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans?category=Simple
Accept: application/json

### Vans - get all (category filter: Luxury + price range)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans?category=Luxury&minPrice=100&maxPrice=250
Accept: application/json

### Vans - get one by id
# 1) Run a "get all" request first
# 2) Copy a van "id" and paste it below
@VanId = 73a10d33-7da4-4f0a-b58d-0d0efc5e70e3000
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans/{{VanId}}
Accept: application/json

### Rent a van (days query)
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/vans/{{VanId}}/rent?days=3
Accept: application/json

###
### Auth - sign up (choose Buyer/Seller/Admin)
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Daisy",
  "lastName": "Sophia",
  "email": "daisy@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!",
  "role": "Buyer"
}

### Auth - buyer login
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login/buyer
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com",
  "password": "Buyer123!"
}

### Auth - seller login
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login/seller
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "seller@vanlife.com",
  "password": "Seller123!"
}

### Auth - admin login
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@vanlife.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Auth - forgot password
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com"
}

### Auth - reset password
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@vanlife.com",
  "newPassword": "NewBuyer123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewBuyer123!"
}

###
### Seller dashboard
@SellerId = 2cb91a52-42b5-4f59-9f3a-a96925f90488

### Seller - get seller vans (not all)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/seller/{{SellerId}}/dashboard/vans
Accept: application/json

### Seller - income (optional days filter)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/seller/{{SellerId}}/dashboard/income?days=30
Accept: application/json

### Seller - specific van management view (visibility/pricing/photos)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/seller/vans/{{VanId}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Reviews (seller/buyer)
@UserId = {{SellerId}}

### Reviews - all for user
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/reviews/users/{{UserId}}
Accept: application/json

### Reviews - date filter + type filter
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/reviews/users/{{UserId}}?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&reviewType=Positive
Accept: application/json

###
### Finance
### Income graph (year filter)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/finance/income-graph?year=2026
Accept: application/json

### Transactions (days filter)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/finance/transactions?days=14
Accept: application/json

###
### Images
### Upload (fake URL returned; no actual file upload in this beginner version)
POST {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images/upload?fileName=van-photo.jpg
Accept: application/json

### List uploaded images
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images
Accept: application/json

### Delete image by id
@ImageId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
DELETE {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/api/images/{{ImageId}}
Accept: application/json

###
### 404 test (any unknown endpoint)
GET {{VanLife.Api_HostAddress}}/this-does-not-exist
Accept: application/json
